      <preface xml:id="preface">
        <title>How to Use This Book</title>
        <p>
          Welcome to <em>Data and Statistics: A Choose Your Own Adventure</em>! 
          This is not a traditional textbook. Instead, you will make decisions 
          that guide your learning journey through the world of statistics.
        </p>
        <p>
          <alert>How it works:</alert>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <p>
                You will encounter scenarios and questions that require you to 
                analyze data or apply statistical concepts.
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <p>
                Work through the problems on your own (using paper, calculator, 
                or statistical software outside this book).
              </p>
            </li>
            <li>
